item.title: How i can change this:
item.dc:creator: @VorargC VorargC
item.description:
@VorargC wrote:

In player.java…
find these

playerEquipment[playerHat]=2581; playerEquipment[playerCape]=1052; playerEquipment[playerAmulet]=6585; playerEquipment[playerChest]=3140; playerEquipment[playerShield]=3844; playerEquipment[playerLegs]=4730; playerEquipment[playerHands]=7462; playerEquipment[playerFeet]=2577; playerEquipment[playerRing]=6735; playerEquipment[playerArrows]=-1; playerEquipment[playerWeapon]=4151;
Change the numbers to the item numbers you want to start with.
